      <title>标准普尔表示，南非动用储备可能会损害央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/south-africa-may-harm-central-bank-by-tapping-reserves-s-p-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级公司的分析师警告说，南非决定利用该国黄金和外汇储备的利润来抑制债务水平，可能会影响央行的独立性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/south-africa-may-harm-central-bank-by-tapping-reserves-s-p-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
