    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚银行的现金储备将减缓顶级贷款机构的贷款增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-banks-cash-reserves-to-slow-loan-growth-for-top-lenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于该行业面临流动性状况趋紧，尼日利亚对其银行监管现金储备要求的大幅提高可能会使最大银行的贷款增长速度减半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-banks-cash-reserves-to-slow-loan-growth-for-top-lenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行表示银行需要改善交易客户风险控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/ecb-says-banks-need-to-improve-trading-client-risk-controls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级监管官员表示，欧洲银行需要提高管理与对冲基金等客户打交道时面临的风险的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/ecb-says-banks-need-to-improve-trading-client-risk-controls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:40:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
