      <title>Ageas 概述以 31 亿英镑收购英国保险公司 Direct Line</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/uk-insurer-direct-line-said-to-reject-ageas-takeover-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Direct Line Insurance Group Plc 表示，其董事会一致拒绝了富杰斯的收购要约，称该收购要约“不确定”且“没有吸引力”。]]></description>
